OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunny spells
OL,7,Fthen long clear spells overnight.
OL,8,FCloud increases towards dawn with
OL,9,Fperhaps a little rain for Kintyre and
OL,10,Fthe Isles later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSome early brightness for
OL,13,FAyrshire and Lanarkshire, otherwise a
OL,14,Fmostly cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain, occasionally heavy especially
OL,16,Facross Argyll. The rain turns more
OL,17,Fshowery in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
